############################
#     1. Introduction      #
############################

 Name: NOVP FFmpeg v1.4.0.8
 Description: FFmpeg fork from Splayer with frame accuracy options

 Licensing          -> LICENSE
 
 To clone the repository with all the submodules use 
   git clone --recursive git://github.com/bor0/NOVP_FFmpeg

 After cloning, make sure to apply FFmpeg.patch

############################
#        2. Build          #
############################

Mac OS X:
  1. make -C libffmpeg

Windows (to be fixed):
  1. Launch mingw
  2. Write make -C libffmpeg
  3. Launch genwinlib.cmd to convert the generated libraries to MSVC format

NOTE: To clean, run clean.sh
NOTE: To force make, write "make -B -C libffmpeg"

